sequenceDiagram
  participant L as learning
  participant P as progress
  participant A as achievement
  participant M as monitoring

  Note over L: L'enfant soumet une réponse

  L->>L: Mission.submitAnswer()
  L->>P: ExerciseCompleted(childId, score, duration, confusions)

  P->>P: ProgressRecord.recordActivity()
  P->>P: StatCalculator.computeDaily()
  P->>M: ActivityRecorded(childId, activity)

  M->>M: Dashboard mise à jour (timeline)

  L->>A: MissionCompleted(childId, missionId, totalScore)

  A->>A: Player.awardXP(amount)
  A->>A: LevelCalculator.computeLevel()
  A->>A: BadgeEvaluator.evaluate()

  alt Badge débloqué
    A->>M: BadgeUnlocked(childId, badge)
    M->>M: Alert(SUCCESS, Nouveau badge!)
    M-->>M: NotificationSender.sendToObserver(parent)
  end

  alt Level up
    A->>M: LevelUp(childId, oldLevel, newLevel)
    M-->>M: NotificationSender.sendToObserver(parent)
  end
